00:00:03.919 --> 00:00:06.250
How to Cook Fava Beans.

00:00:06.250 --> 00:00:09.929
There are many delicious recipes you can make
with fava beans once you get them out of the

00:00:09.929 --> 00:00:10.929
pod.

00:00:10.929 --> 00:00:15.269
Fava beans have a nutty, buttery taste and
complement a number of other flavors.

00:00:15.269 --> 00:00:25.570
You will need Fava beans 2 1/4 pounds baby
artichokes Lemon juice Olive oil Leek Garlic

00:00:25.570 --> 00:00:34.530
Salt and pepper Red pepper flakes Flat leaf
parsley Thyme Pita bread Corn 2 cucumbers

00:00:34.530 --> 00:00:44.799
Onions 2 oz. feta cheese Mediterranean vinaigrette
Red bell pepper Tarragon Tomato and ground

00:00:44.799 --> 00:00:46.190
cumin.

00:00:46.190 --> 00:00:47.539
Step 1.

00:00:47.539 --> 00:00:52.489
Shell the fava beans, discard the pods, and
then remove the peels from the beans by slitting

00:00:52.489 --> 00:00:55.670
them with a knife and popping out the beans.

00:00:55.670 --> 00:00:59.909
Then you can cook them until they're soft
by boiling them in salted water, blanch them

00:00:59.909 --> 00:01:05.920
by boiling them and then submerging them in
ice water, or steam them for 10 minutes.

00:01:05.920 --> 00:01:07.320
Step 2.

00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:10.700
Pair the fava beans with stewed baby artichokes.

00:01:10.700 --> 00:01:15.719
Remove the outer leaves from the artichokes,
trim and peel the stems, rub them with lemon,

00:01:15.719 --> 00:01:21.280
and place them in a bath of 4 cups water with
3 tablespoons lemon juice.

00:01:21.280 --> 00:01:22.280
Step 3.

00:01:22.280 --> 00:01:25.700
Heat 2 teaspoons olive oil over medium heat.

00:01:25.700 --> 00:01:31.679
Then add the chopped leek, three cloves crushed
garlic, a teaspoon salt, and a quarter teaspoon

00:01:31.679 --> 00:01:34.579
each black pepper and red pepper flakes.

00:01:34.579 --> 00:01:36.290
Cook for two minutes.

00:01:36.290 --> 00:01:37.729
Step 4.

00:01:37.729 --> 00:01:43.509
Add the artichokes, lemon water, and four
sprigs each flat parsley and thyme.

00:01:43.509 --> 00:01:45.909
Reduce the heat and simmer for 15 minutes.

00:01:45.909 --> 00:01:49.619
Add the beans, cook for three minutes, and
serve hot.

00:01:49.619 --> 00:01:53.319
Serve with pita bread for dipping and scooping.

00:01:53.319 --> 00:01:54.320
Step 5.

00:01:54.320 --> 00:02:00.429
Toss 1 pound cooked fava beans and 2 cups
cooked corn kernels with a sliced cucumber,

00:02:00.429 --> 00:02:06.750
1/2 cup thinly sliced red onion, 2 tablespoons
chopped parsley, and 2 ounces crumbled feta

00:02:06.750 --> 00:02:08.200
cheese.

00:02:08.200 --> 00:02:09.960
Serve with a Mediterranean vinaigrette.

00:02:09.960 --> 00:02:14.840
You can find many Mediterranean vinaigrette
recipes online.

00:02:14.840 --> 00:02:16.580
Step 6.

00:02:16.580 --> 00:02:22.940
Make succotash by sauteing 2 tablespoons finely
diced white onion in 2 tablespoons olive oil

00:02:22.940 --> 00:02:24.760
over low heat.

00:02:24.760 --> 00:02:30.849
When the onion is translucent, raise the heat
and add a peeled, seeded, and chopped cucumber.

00:02:30.849 --> 00:02:33.040
Cook for six minutes.

00:02:33.040 --> 00:02:34.050
Step 7.

00:02:34.050 --> 00:02:38.239
Add 1 cup corn kernels and cook for two minutes.

00:02:38.239 --> 00:02:45.530
Add 1 cup cooked fava beans, 1/2 cup diced
red bell pepper, and salt and pepper to taste.

00:02:45.530 --> 00:02:50.280
Cook for two more minutes, add two teaspoons
fresh, chopped tarragon, and serve.

00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:52.030
Step 8.

00:02:52.030 --> 00:02:58.370
Pour the beans into a pot and bring to a boil.

00:02:58.370 --> 00:03:05.510
Mix them well and add one chopped onion, one
diced tomato, 1 tablespoon olive oil, 1 tablespoon

00:03:05.510 --> 00:03:12.730
ground cumin, 1/4 cup chopped parsley, 1/4
cup lemon juice, salt and pepper, and ground

00:03:12.730 --> 00:03:15.069
red pepper to taste.

00:03:15.069 --> 00:03:16.189
Step 9.

00:03:16.189 --> 00:03:21.160
Bring the mixture back to a boil, and then
reduce the heat to medium.

00:03:21.160 --> 00:03:25.470
Let the mixture cook for five minutes and
serve warm with grilled pita bread.

00:03:25.470 --> 00:03:31.470
Did you know Many ancient societies thought
fava beans possessed spiritual and magical

00:03:31.470 --> 00:03:32.849
properties.

